# Blue Nile Bangle Bracelets Review {{year}}: Italian Gold, Diamond & Lab-Grown, Ranked

Blue Nile's bangle collection runs from an $805 James Allen twisted gold bangle to a $10,610 three-carat diamond Luna piece — and the highest-reviewed styles are not the diamond ones. They're the solid Italian gold bangles, which have been on the page the longest and accumulated the most verified buyer feedback.

Before I rank every style: I need to tell you something about buying bangles online that almost no review site covers, because they're afraid it'll cost them affiliate clicks. **Bangles are fixed-diameter rigid circles. Unlike a chain bracelet, you cannot add an extender. If the inner diameter doesn't slide over your knuckles, it doesn't fit — period.** I'm putting this upfront because an ill-fitting bangle is a $2,000–$5,000 mistake that is not your fault but is entirely preventable with a 30-second measurement.

### TL;DR: Blue Nile Bangles — Farzana's Bottom Line

- **Most Reviewed:** [Twist Bangle in 14k Italian Yellow Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/twist-bangle-in-14k-italian-yellow-gold-item-196012?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — 22 reviews, ~~$3,175~~ **$2,699** (15% off)
- **Best Value Under $1,100:** [Polished Bangle in 14k Yellow Gold by James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/polished-bangle-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-by-james-allen-item-304583?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — 4 reviews, $1,070
- **Best Diamond Deal:** [Single Row Diamond Bangle in 14K White Gold by James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/single-row-bangle-diamond-bracelet-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-315788?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — ~~$2,970~~ **$1,782** (40% off) — biggest discount on the page
- **Best Cuff Deal:** [Criss Cross Cuff Diamond Bracelet by James Allen](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/criss-cross-cuff-diamond-bracelet-in-14k-white-gold-by-james-allen-item-310864?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — ~~$2,810~~ **$1,967** (30% off), 6 reviews, in 3 metals
- **Best Statement Piece Under $3,500:** [Diamond Station Bangle in 14k Yellow Gold (1/4 ct. tw.)](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/diamond-station-bangle-bracelet-in-14k-yellow-gold-1-4-ct-tw-item-195836?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) — 17 reviews, $3,460
