| [Twist Bangle 14k Italian White Gold](https://www.bluenile.com/jewelry/bracelets/twist-bangle-in-14k-italian-white-gold-item-201150?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blue_nile_reviews) | ~~$3,085~~ | **$2,622** (-15%) | Shop |

